'''別里貝蜥屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Belebay''）是種已滅絕[[副爬行動物|副爬行動物]]，是[[波羅蜥科|波羅蜥科]]的一屬，生存於[[二疊紀|二疊紀]]早中期的[[法國|法國]]、[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]與[[中國|中國]]。生存年代最早是二疊紀最早期（[[阿舍爾階|阿舍爾階]]），最晚是二疊紀中期<ref name=B.chengi>{{cite journal |author=Johannes Müller, Jin-Ling Li and Robert R. Reisz |year=2008 |title=A new bolosaurid parareptile, ''Belebey chengi'' sp. nov., from the Middle Permian of China and its paleogeographic significance |url=http://www.springerlink.com/content/h552477060636055/ |journal=Naturwissenschaften |volume=95 |issue=12 |pages=1169–1174 |doi=10.1007/s00114-008-0438-0 }}{{Dead link|date=2020年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name=Parareptilia2>{{cite journal |author=Marcello Ruta, Juan C. Cisneros, Torsten Liebrect, Linda A. Tsuji and Johannes Muller |year=2011 |title=Amniotes through major biological crises: faunal turnover among Parareptiles and the end-Permian mass extinction |journal=Palaeontology |volume=54 |issue=5 |pages=1117–1137 |doi=10.1111/j.1475-4983.2011.01051.x}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |authors=Jocelyn Falconnet |year=2012 |title=First evidence of a bolosaurid parareptile in France (latest Carboniferous-earliest Permian of the Autun basin) and the spatiotemporal distribution of the Bolosauridae |journal=Bulletin de la Société Géologique de France |volume=183 |issue=6 |pages=495–508 |url=http://bsgf.geoscienceworld.org/content/183/6/495.abstract |doi=10.2113/gssgfbull.183.6.495 |access-date=2013-01-22 |archive-date=2016-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160601191340/http://bsgf.geoscienceworld.org/content/183/6/495.abstract |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

